      "id": "PopularPost356376",
      "post_content": "I'll just repost what someone else said on [Marath, Will of the Wild](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Marath, Will of the Wild)'s discussion page: this + [Cathars' Crusade](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cathars' Crusade) + [Marath, Will of the Wild](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Marath, Will of the Wild). As long as you only make 1/1s, Crusade keeps Marathi replenished, and then you can sac one token to this for enough nana to make two more. Infinite 1/1s!",
